Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:04.47,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Time is a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.03,0:00:06.55,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:14.55,Inuboku-main,Woman1,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know "Ayakashi Kan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:14.55,Inuboku-overlap,Woman2,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.55,0:00:15.65,Inuboku-main,Woman3,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Maison de Ayakashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:17.40,Inuboku-overlap,Woman4,0000,0000,0000,,They say the security is unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:17.91,Inuboku-main,Woman1,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that celebrity complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.37,0:00:21.75,Inuboku-thoughts-onscreen,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I've got a bad habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.13,0:00:23.26,Inuboku-main,Woman4,0000,0000,0000,,The one where each apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.26,0:00:25.31,Inuboku-main,Woman4,0000,0000,0000,,gets one member of the Secret Service, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:27.00,Inuboku-main,Woman1,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently she's a new tenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:28.63,Inuboku-main,Woman3,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "Secret Service"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:29.84,Inuboku-main,Woman4,0000,0000,0000,,A bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:31.86,Inuboku-main,Woman2,0000,0000,0000,,I hear she's the daughter of an old family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:33.71,Inuboku-main,Woman1,0000,0000,0000,,A huge conglomerate called Shirakiin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:35.80,Inuboku-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're the center of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:37.97,Inuboku-thoughts-onscreen,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I've been doing it since I was little,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:39.85,Inuboku-thoughts-onscreen,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I've been doing it since I was little,\Nand it's not something\N I can control.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.36,0:00:42.42,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Should getting attention from
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.42,0:00:44.30,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,those bored housewives make me happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:47.84,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be the \Ngossip fodder of their circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:50.23,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just do your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:51.62,Inuboku-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:55.24,Inuboku-thoughts-onscreen,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I will put up a bold front
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:56.99,Inuboku-thoughts-onscreen,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I will put up a bold front\Nand verbally abuse people\N for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:03.33,Inuboku-thoughts-onscreen,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is my bad habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.47,0:01:08.37,Inuboku-main,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ririchiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:10.67,Inuboku-main,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:12.13,Inuboku-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Sorinozuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:14.05,Inuboku-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't seen you in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.53,0:01:17.57,Inuboku-main,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Loathing yourself for your own \Ngroundless hostility again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:19.54,Inuboku-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:21.30,Inuboku-main,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you brought?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.30,0:01:22.68,Inuboku-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,They're bringing the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.94,0:01:25.89,Inuboku-main,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:28.83,Inuboku-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act all worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.83,0:01:32.52,Inuboku-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We lived close to each other, \Nbut that's all we've got in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:34.40,Inuboku-main,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,But I know lots about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:35.82,Inuboku-main,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Like back in the sixth grade...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.29,0:01:38.57,Inuboku-flashback,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Ririchiyo, want to come eat lunch with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.52,0:01:42.16,Inuboku-flashback,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing but sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:43.48,Inuboku-main,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Is what you said to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:44.84,Inuboku-main,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,but you cried about it afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.84,0:01:47.74,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't crying! \NThat was an allergic reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:51.06,Inuboku-main,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,You wrote a really polite apology\N letter after we got in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:51.81,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:53.38,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I was just practicing my handwriting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:02:00.38,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,This place has a nickname: Ayakashi Kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:02.85,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Its real name is Maison de Ayakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:07.50,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,An apartment complex for the super elite,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:09.21,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,where only chosen people may live.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:12.74,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the public is supposed to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:30.67,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.33,Inuboku-thoughts-onscreen,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I came here to be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:35.71,Inuboku-thoughts-onscreen,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:41.01,Inuboku-main,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually in room three.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:46.62,Inuboku-main,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me if you need any help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:49.73,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.36,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Room four... this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:12.70,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Am I supposed to thank you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:15.24,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:22.90,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't waste such words on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:26.41,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting so long to meet you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:28.28,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:29.88,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:34.78,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,From this day on,\N it's my duty to oversee your daily safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:37.44,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Soushi Miketsukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.32,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,My daily safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:41.13,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Secret Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.30,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't sign any contracts for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.68,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you don't need me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:47.24,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:48.22,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Then please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:54.14,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I implore you to dispose of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:55.98,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,To... dispose of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:05:03.06,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I exist only for you, \Nso if you say you do not need me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:05.28,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,then that renders my life meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.91,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You should value yourself more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:09.28,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You are so incredibly kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:09.28,Inuboku-overlap,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:12.45,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You are even more wonderful \Nthan I could ever have imagined!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:16.12,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Please, make me your servant— No,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:18.31,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,your dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:23.92,Inuboku-ep-title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,The Dog and Me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:29.09,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo, about those fish bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:30.06,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:34.52,Inuboku-main,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Ririchiyo, you hired someone \Nfrom the Secret Service?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.68,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:39.36,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Someone in my family must have \Nset this up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:40.84,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:44.78,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,they had to find someone so hard to abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.74,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But the whole reason I came here was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:52.56,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anyone from the Secret Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:54.75,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just terminate your contract right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:55.48,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:56.50,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:01.24,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,But what else do I have to live for,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:03.52,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,if my raison d'etre is to serve you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.94,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Just go back to whatever you \Nwere doing before yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:07.22,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,That life is dead to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:08.29,Inuboku-main,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no biggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:09.89,Inuboku-main,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,So you got a pretty bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.64,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You are too random!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:14.28,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Just ignore me when my \Npresence inconveniences you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:17.36,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I will be happy to be used\N by you only when it suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:19.27,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Will that really make you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:21.03,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:23.63,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I've known you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:27.44,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting to meet you for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:28.87,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You know... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.74,Inuboku-main,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:34.22,Inuboku-main,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that big, \Nand there is a lot of activity...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.16,Inuboku-main,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,in our community.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:42.75,Inuboku-flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:03.04,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I let my guard down \Nsince it's spring break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:04.36,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's already nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:20.46,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't shop for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:23.05,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll get something \Nto eat in the lounge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.25,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,A lot happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:28.88,Inuboku-flashback,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the contract is void.\N Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:33.02,Inuboku-flashback,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,So I probably won't see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.31,Inuboku-flashback,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Stop looking at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:41.56,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not even he will show up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:44.81,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Miss Ririchiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.71,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're looking beautiful today, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:56.99,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Your beauty truly suits your name well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.32,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:08:01.16,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I have not been told your waking hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.59,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,so I have been waiting here \Nsince six in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:04.53,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Since six?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:05.36,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.09,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Spring just started... it's still cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:08.34,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:10.35,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,But when I thought that you might
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:12.65,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,be opening your door any \Nmoment and stepping out,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.26,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,the cold became irrelevant to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:15.14,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, the faithful dog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:18.75,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:21.51,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,If you need to talk to me,\N just wake me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:22.98,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You are too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:26.84,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't want the hassle of you \Ncroaking in front of my door.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:27.90,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I will be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:31.97,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,To know that I have even the\N smallest place in your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.32,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,makes freezing to death seem a fine—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:34.32,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, the faithful dog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:37.23,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be breakfasting in the lounge?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:40.33,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you, \N"I don't need your services."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:44.75,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Today's menu features \Na bagel sandwich with salad,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:46.66,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,and fruit yogurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:48.58,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I don't need your fussing,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:51.45,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,and then you do even more?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.54,Inuboku-main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,The dressing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:08.94,Inuboku-main,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:11.80,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:14.52,Inuboku-main,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:15.65,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:19.63,Inuboku-main,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Karuta Roromiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.36,Inuboku-main,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with the Secret Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:26.93,Inuboku-main,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,My client is in room two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:30.29,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ririchiyo Shirakiin, from room four.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:32.25,Inuboku-main,Car,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.41,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, whatever, I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:41.34,Inuboku-main,Car,0000,0000,0000,,A symbol of our acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:47.93,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.81,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,That was another Secret\N Service agent, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:55.52,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,We could take a little \Nstroll inside the complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:57.40,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I'd give you a tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.76,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I keep telling you,\N I'm fine by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.58,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for bringing my food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.93,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what I'm saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:05.91,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, that's very polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:09.29,Inuboku-main,Soushil,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you allow me to be your guide?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:12.24,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at sucking people into your pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:13.50,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You're crafty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:16.92,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You are an honest and wonderful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:24.98,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,This is the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:27.19,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,There are baths in each room as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:29.40,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,but this might be nice for a change of scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:32.23,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Directly above the bath, we have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:33.75,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It's the rooftop garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:35.86,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,With its spacious skies and relaxing gardens,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:38.81,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this place will be perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:40.60,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,if you ever need somewhere to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.88,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,The stream under this little stone bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:44.49,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,is made from pebbles, which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:50.37,Inuboku-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Meh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:51.49,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Meh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:54.59,Inuboku-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,This is too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:10:58.76,Inuboku-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Your black hair, your white skin,\N your almond-shaped eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.36,Inuboku-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your slenderness and small stature,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:01.67,Inuboku-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,your black tights look so supple!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:03.21,Inuboku-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You... are too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:04.65,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:07.85,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Secret Service's Nobara Yukinokouji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:10.01,Inuboku-main,Bara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how could I do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:13.39,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,This is Miss Ririchiyo Shirakiin,\N who moved in here yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:16.24,Inuboku-main,Bara,0000,0000,0000,,Ririchiyo. That's a strange name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:17.28,Inuboku-main,Bara,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty special.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:22.41,Inuboku-main,Bara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sorinozuka's Secret Service agent.\NMy name is Nobara Yukinokouji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:26.20,Inuboku-main,Bara,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we will become... good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:29.12,Inuboku-main,Bara,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I mean in a sexual way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.62,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Sexual?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:35.26,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't her openness refreshing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.03,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Openness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:44.26,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's a word that has no meaning for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:58.82,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm uncertain,\N the past comes to hunt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:03.84,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:08.27,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I knew your waking hour, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:15.27,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Your herbal tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:22.59,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:31.02,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,They say that lavender \Nhas a natural calming effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:36.06,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,The light was on late in your\N room these last two nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:43.00,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You said you knew me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:44.53,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that knowledge repulse you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:49.71,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,The Shirakiin family has been
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.71,0:12:51.87,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,a honorable and rich family for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:53.65,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It is the house where I am from.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:56.26,Inuboku-flashback,Ghosts,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Miss Ririchiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:12:59.75,Inuboku-flashback,child,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you're special!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:02.17,Inuboku-flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,All your house has is money!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:04.45,Inuboku-flashback,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,You're so boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.85,Inuboku-flashback,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:10.39,Inuboku-flashback,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:13.27,Inuboku-flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It's no trouble at all. \NAfter all, I am her teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:17.65,Inuboku-flashback,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I will make sure to pass \Non your name to our master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.36,Inuboku-flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:25.20,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I was lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.98,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Both because of being bullied \Nfor being a Shirakiin,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:30.70,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,and for being protected by the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:34.14,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:36.65,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the house I am part of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:39.13,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,is a bigger part of me than myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:42.00,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:45.55,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you've felt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:49.72,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,To think that all along, \Nyou've been carrying this burden alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:51.42,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:52.13,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:55.46,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:01.24,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You cry easily, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:07.28,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I think I got my bad habit\N sometime around then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:09.72,Inuboku-flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're so boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:13.41,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Those words were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:19.51,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I was weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:23.68,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was fit into the\N mold of the Shirakiin family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:29.80,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I was lonely and felt pathetic,\N so I put up a front.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.98,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,However, I know I have to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.42,0:14:34.94,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I have to learn how to
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:37.77,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,build up my confidence so that\N I can properly interact with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.81,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be alone until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:42.90,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, all I do is hurt people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:44.69,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:49.19,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay with me, \Nsooner or later you'll get hurt, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.54,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we try it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:12.42,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,And you know, you are even\N cuter than I ever imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:16.02,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You are a wonderful person who\N honors justice and you're a bit shy—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:17.18,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Just stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:37.87,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose he is a good person,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:41.29,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,but I've got to keep my focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:45.29,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,If I start to enjoy myself,\NI'll only get myself hurt again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:47.21,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,The cycle will just begin anew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:54.59,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,A blackout...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.11,Inuboku-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:04.13,Inuboku-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the high security \Ncelebrity complex, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:05.48,Inuboku-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.91,Inuboku-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you're going to quietly\N take me to your room
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.06,Inuboku-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,and give me all your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:14.37,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're just a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:15.57,Inuboku-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:21.41,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite unlucky to have come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:28.50,Inuboku-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Her eyes... are glowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:32.59,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,This house isn't guarded against mere humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:36.44,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,After all, your kind are not a threat to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.23,Inuboku-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:40.06,Inuboku-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:56.35,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:02.58,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You dared to point a\N gun at Miss Ririchiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.77,Inuboku-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,M-Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.53,Inuboku-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:28.73,Inuboku-main,Bara,0000,0000,0000,,Monster? How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:31.73,Inuboku-main,Bara,0000,0000,0000,,We're proper humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:34.94,Inuboku-main,Bara,0000,0000,0000,,But one of our ancestors had \Nmingled with monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:37.07,Inuboku-main,Bara,0000,0000,0000,,We're just channeling them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:41.13,Inuboku-main,Bara,0000,0000,0000,,We attract the attention \Nof pure-blooded monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:43.71,Inuboku-main,Bara,0000,0000,0000,,which is why we decided to build this place
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:46.21,Inuboku-main,Bara,0000,0000,0000,,where we can live together\N and help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:49.25,Inuboku-main,Bara,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want a mere burglar \Ncalling me "monster."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:51.33,Inuboku-main,Bara,0000,0000,0000,,And you're filthy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:54.40,Inuboku-main,Bara,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't it at least have \Nbeen three sisters in leotards?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:56.01,Inuboku-main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Your fantasies are running wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:59.13,Inuboku-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what the hell \Nyou're talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:00.96,Inuboku-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm telling you, just keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:14.61,Inuboku-main,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:17.77,Inuboku-main,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:31.54,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:35.37,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:39.23,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I wasn't thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:40.72,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Please take my left hand then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:41.51,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:44.08,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:48.02,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I exist to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:48.99,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:51.58,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's always Miss Ririchiyo this,\N Miss Ririchiyo that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:52.88,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You even got yourself hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:56.21,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how much you want to be a dog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:58.66,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You want to put yourself on the line for that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.99,0:19:10.64,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:13.34,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,A kiss on the tip of the nail is a sign of loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:16.52,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason I am here
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:20.26,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,is my loyalty to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.71,0:19:23.22,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It is irrelevant, whether you are
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:26.29,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,the daughter of a great house or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:30.76,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I told you when we first met,\N that I have always known you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:34.40,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,As you are the one who saved me, \NI owe you all my respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:37.59,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You and nobody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:40.40,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know how desperately\N I've wanted to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.69,0:19:42.68,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,And now I've failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:44.20,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I will do absolutely everything in my power
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:46.26,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,to make it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:52.80,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,So please, please,\N will you let me stay by your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:58.49,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:01.77,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You won't listen to what I say anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:03.69,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:05.04,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I am like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.84,0:20:07.46,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares what you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:09.52,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Just go where you want\Nand live the way you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:12.33,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:15.52,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:19.39,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I am not worthy, \Nbut please bear with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:25.15,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of my leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:31.09,Inuboku-main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I was pretty freaked out yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:33.63,Inuboku-main,Car,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:35.07,Inuboku-main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} were scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:36.04,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:39.21,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you got a good night's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:40.96,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I was simply tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:44.22,Inuboku-main,Bara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sorinozuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:46.37,Inuboku-main,Bara,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this your core?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:47.55,Inuboku-main,Sori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:49.64,Inuboku-main,Sori,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:52.02,Inuboku-main,Bara,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make trouble for the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:53.26,Inuboku-main,Sori,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:57.35,Inuboku-main,Sori,0000,0000,0000,,This form is so much more relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:20:59.84,Inuboku-main,Sori,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, there's so much you have to \Ndo properly in your human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:02.07,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What part of you was proper again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:02.65,pink,txt,0000,0000,0000,,- Shaggy, unkempt hair
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:02.65,pink2,txt,0000,0000,0000,,- Track suit every day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:02.65,pink3,txt,0000,0000,0000,,- Sandals
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:05.61,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Mr. Sorinozuka is a \N"Flying cloth monster."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:06.32,Inuboku-main,sori,0000,0000,0000,,This is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:09.76,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What, you live in the same \Ncomplex and you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:14.77,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I only moved in here \Nthe day before you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.05,0:21:19.92,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,So it was just a coincidence\N that they hired you for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:21.59,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.50,0:21:24.77,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,it was not a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:28.55,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I am in the same place as you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:32.22,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,and you have granted me \Npermission to do so, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:34.41,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.41,0:21:36.45,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, it wasn't a coincidence at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.45,0:21:37.63,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You are such a wonderful person
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:40.02,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,with such a high sense of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.35,0:21:43.69,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You would never go \Nback on your word, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:45.70,pure black,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,1)}Pure\N Black
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:47.45,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:47.36,pledge,Text,0000,0000,0000,,I
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:47.61,pledge,Text,0000,0000,0000,,I pled
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:47.87,pledge,Text,0000,0000,0000,,I pledged
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:48.20,pledge,Text,0000,0000,0000,,I pledged some
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:48.87,pledge,Text,0000,0000,0000,,I pledged something
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:49.74,pledge,Text,0000,0000,0000,,I pledged something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:51.85,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Could you be... You're a stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:55.30,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. I am your dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:21:58.74,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,After this, I will remember it again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.66,0:22:05.26,Inuboku-internal/narration,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It was the beginning of a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.80,0:23:41.28,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.28,0:23:43.36,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing that makes me happier
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:45.06,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,than being able to serve you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.06,0:23:48.56,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,but I have to say, \Nyou are truly beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.56,0:23:50.71,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost as if the \Nword "beauty" came alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.71,0:23:53.38,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,and materialized and that is—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.38,0:23:54.73,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Stop flattering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.73,0:23:56.35,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to be \Nannouncing the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.35,0:23:59.27,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,There is no worth in \Ntalking about the preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.27,0:24:00.84,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,when your beauty is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.84,0:24:06.70,Inuboku-main,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,My humble mouth wants to praise\N your beauty for all of eternity...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.19,0:24:08.92,Inuboku-next-ep-title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,A Lonely Dog
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.70,0:24:07.87,Inuboku-main,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Just stop already!
